{"tid":1320063,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得有人帶緊撐狗風向？","createTime":"2019-07-15T09:53:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T14:53:19.000Z","uid":16811,"like":162,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"5883380424a4a1640366fa1bbfbe643c1489e824","tid":1320063,"uid":16811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:53:50.000Z","msg":"唔知點解今日好多人突然想同情班前線狗<br />\n其實係咪唔記得哂6.12發生咩事？<br />\n上水果個中學生差D跌落去既事？<br />\n有幾多個手足行過屌狗之後比人拉左？<br />\n畫家唔比保釋比人玩到喊？<br />\n仲有好多好多<br />\n<br />\n我想講有好多人比狗打係無辜<br />\n但班狗起勢咁打 你話打一兩棍交差都算<br />\n大家諗下點解啦 真心想改過既又點會咁<br />\n<br />\n以為可以感化到 唔該你去感化林鄭 慢慢同佢傾<br />\n我都想好想世界和平 香港人connect哂<br />\n但現實世界未必係大家諗到咁浪漫<br />\n<br />\n希望大家諗下之前發生咩事<br />\n自己再判斷下啦<br />\n香港人好善忘嫁<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />各有各做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自推一頁 冇人聽我講就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a9d88727675a17656f7bc847ca9377e94e55e4d","tid":1320063,"uid":16811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:54:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"342b288024b73fca93b5688c99e375597565a4ab","tid":1320063,"uid":244876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:54:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1320014/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1320014/page/1</a><br />\n狗狗聽主人唔同指令實在好大壓力，應該就來爆煲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係時候搵傳心師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6613e6536b9f1b022f6280dd47b3ba781dc3ad2","tid":1320063,"uid":16811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T09:56:32.000Z","msg":"<img sr