覺得琴晚示威者嘅行為好合情理"},{"pid":"2a5c4489d6900dfb04c7bdb318eb8cdea991494d","tid":1320063,"uid":16811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f03159a6f49e0546cf6d0ed235cd1fb2f2196e97","tid":1320063,"uid":262342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:14:44.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:17:16.000Z","msg":"想講唔做狗其實仲有好多出路<br />\n<br />\n入境海關消防<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你想安全就咪做狗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42ab2ff22abc575f6cddd7a81e6ac0587366c9e7","tid":1320063,"uid":16811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b335464fa6defa1ebc39d915c95c4fca1113038c","tid":1320063,"uid":70531,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:16:43.000Z","msg":"預左俾人負評<br />\n<br />\n點解一有唔同嘅意見就一定係帶風向？<br />\n覺得琴晚暴力就一定係撐警？<br />\n其實自己人入面唔洗一定所有野都係同樣想法<br />\n有唔同意嘅地方而又講得出原因就正正表現我地同班冇腦盲撐政府藍絲嘅唔同 我地會用腦 有自己嘅立場，底線同道德觀 呢樣都係我地比佢地優勝嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n真係唔該唔好一見到呢啲就屌 只會令人更加唔信服<br />\n<br />\n利申覺得琴晚示威者嘅行為好合情理"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:20:50.000Z","msg":"我冇屌到 只係問下有冇人咁覺得姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係我主要係講同情狗呢樣野好有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇人逼你做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你想人比返尊嚴你就唔該辭職啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3490e2b00f602ae1513ee940b4e737dc231a57c","tid":1320063,"uid":16811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:21:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e43eda3082952c008c189d52dc93a3d8309cd155","tid":1320063,"uid":37875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:21:16.