 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇人逼你做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你想人比返尊嚴你就唔該辭職啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:57:29.000Z","msg":"分化啊，唔係同情。。。<br />\n<br />\n分化 跟 同情係2 樣野，<br />\n我唔使佢地有良心。<br />\n我要佢地散軍心， 就夠"},{"pid":"ebf4fbb829eab582083d45c2d6a48c8e3f6d801f","tid":1320063,"uid":16811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T13:59:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b962de9ca6145373d20cdd7a0b1e9c319ac25695","tid":1320063,"uid":275634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:00:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79295803dfae986d1558bc05aa0f02a5cc837626","tid":1320063,"uid":16811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:00:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9321b391402539cc1c2b7ff3d4e0e9375a014ba6","tid":1320063,"uid":63734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:01:16.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"b506ab5e472601899270a249f6a580b61026ddc0","tid":1320063,"uid":1060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:02:20.000Z","msg":"無論如何都唔可以有人命傷亡<br />\n打還打點到即止好啦"},{"pid":"724c904d3884339aa554596a28bb026f60dc7ac6","tid":1320063,"uid":16811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:04:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/a